75
00:05:41,340 --> 00:05:43,390
I’m no match for Qibao Amber Tribe’s little princess.

76
00:05:45,300 --> 00:05:46,800
Rather than becoming a servant for someone,

77
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:52,370
