93
00:07:42,340 --> 00:07:43,540
He overslept again?

94
00:07:44,050 --> 00:07:45,790
He was still training when I came out.

95
00:07:45,890 --> 00:07:47,110
Maybe he’s still in meditation.

96
00:07:47,550 --> 00:07:49,300
Tang San, bring him here.

97
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:51,450
He must be here for this lesson.

98
00:07:51,550 --> 00:07:52,490
Yes, Dean.

99
00:07:53,340 --> 00:07:54,220
