101
00:08:14,130 --> 00:08:15,120
No, Dean.

102
00:08:15,220 --> 00:08:16,150
Please listen to me.

103
00:08:16,900 --> 00:08:18,410
I’ve reached Level 30!

104
00:08:18,510 --> 00:08:19,350
What?

105
00:08:23,770 --> 00:08:24,450
