158
00:11:24,400 --> 00:11:25,740
Zhu Zhu Qing and I will be at the end.

159
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,970
Follow this formation after we enter the forest,

160
00:11:28,070 --> 00:11:29,610
remain on guard at all times.

161
00:11:38,310 --> 00:11:39,870
Let me warn you again,

162
00:11:40,370 --> 00:11:43,720
Unless you meet a Millennium Soul Beast,
or else I’ll not interfere.

163
00:11:44,310 --> 00:11:46,740
You have to think of strategies on the way.

164
00:11:47,250 --> 00:11:47,830
Yes!

165
00:11:47,940 --> 00:11:49,720
Alright, let’s go.

166
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:51,370
Oscar.

167
00:11:52,250 --> 00:11:55,390
Super Recovery Big Sausage!

168
00:12:06,650 --> 00:12:07,940
Run for around two more hours.

169
00:12:08,050 --> 00:12:08,990
There’s a small town in front,

170
00:12:09,100 --> 00:12:10,650
we’ll stay overnight there.

171
00:12:32,750 --> 00:12:34,850
[Soul Land]

172
00:12:54,310 --> 00:12:57,470
I’m so tired after running for the whole day.

173
00:13:00,150 --> 00:13:01,970
Luckily, we have Little Ao’s sausages.

174
00:13:03,550 --> 00:13:05,280
It’s nothing.

175
00:13:05,390 --> 00:13:07,790
Come on, after stuffing so many sausages,

176
00:13:07,890 --> 00:13:08,740
