177
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:10,120
Let’s order for food.

178
00:13:10,230 --> 00:13:11,930
Fatty, you’re always so troublesome.

179
00:13:15,630 --> 00:13:17,550
Why is Teacher Zhao not dining with us?

180
00:13:17,660 --> 00:13:19,420
We have to pay for our expenses outside.

181
00:13:19,520 --> 00:13:20,640
Teachers aren’t allowed

182
00:13:20,750 --> 00:13:22,870
