a quote for monsters.

197
00:15:08,260 --> 00:15:11,560
Cang Hui School is an
Advanced Soul Master School, right?

198
00:15:44,210 --> 00:15:45,520
Don’t waste the food.

199
00:15:50,650 --> 00:15:51,730
My apology.

200
00:16:11,920 --> 00:16:14,500
I’m sorry, my hand slipped.

201
00:16:35,820 --> 00:16:36,870
It’s so delicious.

202
00:16:46,800 --> 00:16:48,810
Which school you guys come from?

203
00:16:49,650 --> 00:16:50,680
Trying to interrogate us?

204
00:16:50,780 --> 00:16:52,130
You’re still unworthy.

205
00:16:54,790 --> 00:16:55,530
This is good.

206
00:16:57,490 --> 00:16:59,630
Tastes fine, lacking some skills though.

207
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:02,210
How arrogant you are!

208
00:17:02,760 --> 00:17:03,840
Teach them a lesson!

209
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:07,120
Fight? I love it.

210
00:17:08,190 --> 00:17:10,020
Hello, brothers.

211
00:17:17,940 --> 00:17:19,930
Hurry and help her,
Xiao Wu is in an unfavorable situation.

212
00:17:29,380 --> 00:17:32,180
Those guys are the one
we should worry about.

213
00:17:51,960 --> 00:17:52,670
