220
00:21:05,170 --> 00:21:08,560
Let me teach you how to be a human.

221
00:21:08,660 --> 00:21:12,830
Remember, we’re not humans but monsters.

222
00:21:19,510 --> 00:21:20,530
Stay on guard.

223
00:21:20,630 --> 00:21:21,450
Be careful!

